# Content Architecture

- Use adapter modules in `src/lib/content` to read data.
- Pages and cards consume adapter output, not raw collection APIs directly.
- Keep article shape stable: `slug`, `title`, `excerpt`, `publishedAt`, `coverImage`, `tags`.
- Store local content in Astro collections under `src/content`.
- If CMS is added later, replace adapter internals and keep component interfaces unchanged.
